---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Breadcrumbs from "../components/Breadcrumbs.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure | CashSpins"
  description="Learn how CashSpins.online earns revenue through affiliate partnerships and how this relates to our editorial independence."
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8 py-12">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: "Home", href: "/" },
      { label: "Affiliate Disclosure" },
    ]} />

    <h1 class="font-headline font-extrabold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-on-surface mt-8 mb-4">
      Affiliate Disclosure
    </h1>
    <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-10">Last updated: April 4, 2026</p>

    <div class="prose">
      <h2>How We Earn Revenue</h2>
      <p>
        CashSpins.online is a free resource for players looking to find the best online casinos,
        bonuses, and gambling guides. To keep this site running and free to use, we participate in
        affiliate partnerships with online casino operators. This means that when you click on certain
        links on our Website and sign up or make a deposit at a casino, we may receive a commission
        from that casino at no additional cost to you.
      </p>

      <h2>How Affiliate Links Work</h2>
      <p>
        Throughout our Website, you will find links marked with buttons such as "Claim Bonus" or
        "Visit Casino." These are affiliate links. When you click on one of these links, a tracking
        cookie is placed on your device so the casino operator can attribute your registration or
        deposit to our referral. This process is standard across the affiliate marketing industry
        and does not affect the price, bonus, or terms you receive from the casino.
      </p>

      <h2>Editorial Independence</h2>
      <p>
        Our editorial team operates independently from our commercial partnerships. Affiliate
        relationships do not influence our ratings, rankings, or reviews. Every casino review on
        CashSpins is based on objective criteria including licensing, game selection, payout speed,
        bonus terms, player complaints, and security measures. We apply the same evaluation framework
        to every casino we review, regardless of whether we have an affiliate relationship with them.
      </p>
      <p>
        If a casino that pays us commissions has poor terms, slow withdrawals, or unresolved player
        complaints, we will say so in our review. Our credibility depends on honest reporting, and
        we take that responsibility seriously.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Trust Matters</h2>
      <p>
        We understand that trust is the foundation of our relationship with our readers. We are
        committed to full transparency about how we earn revenue. If you have any questions about
        our affiliate relationships or editorial process, please contact us at
        <strong>info@cashspins.online</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
